name: A warm storm
description:
I feel lost in my own mind, I don't know what to do with my life while I'm drowning in my thoughts, then I chose to take myself out to sea water to relax But there was a storm when I was about to hit the sea

I'm drowning in thoughts again, and I look out at the sea and start thinking...I should go into the water or go home?

Danger may always happen to me because of a storm, but in another opinion, I don't think I'll ever be able to take another chance like this.

hit the sea while it rains and there's a storm :)

You know, the sea is so warm while there is a storm, I feel like I'm being enclosed by love, warmth from the family, and this is the whole story of this picture "A warm storm"
